  "detailed_description": "Get ready for some fun with our find-a-pair puzzle game! You'll love how it helps improve your memory and attention skills. Whether you're a kid or a bearded guy, this game will have you smiling and thinking in no time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To play, simply click on a stamp to flip it over. Try to find a matching pair. If you don't, don't worry - the stamps will flip back over. The faster you complete each level and the fewer moves you make, the better your final score will be!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Invite your friends to play with you and see who can get the highest score. Who knows, you might just become the memory and attention champion!",
  "about_the_game": "Get ready for some fun with our find-a-pair puzzle game! You'll love how it helps improve your memory and attention skills. Whether you're a kid or a bearded guy, this game will have you smiling and thinking in no time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To play, simply click on a stamp to flip it over. Try to find a matching pair. If you don't, don't worry - the stamps will flip back over. The faster you complete each level and the fewer moves you make, the better your final score will be!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Invite your friends to play with you and see who can get the highest score. Who knows, you might just become the memory and attention champion!",
